Ive never had the original, But I just cant mix enough of this stuff up. Weird and Awesomeness, thats what it is!!&#xD;
Its really good!!&#xD;
&#xD;
The harshness does drop off at about day 4, But I vaped it from the moment that it was mixed!

I've never had the original but this is a really nice summer time vape. Not to sour not to sweet and the peach really makes it pop. I used .75% TFA sweetener to sub for cap SS.&#xD;
&#xD;
Update: after a few days rest the S&amp;V harshness fades and I'm really starting to get addicted to this profile. Definitely adding this to my normal rotation. Thanks
